snippet.title: Vendrán las aves - A slice-of-life tamagotchi about burnout!
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://deconstructeam.itch.io/vendran-las-aves?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt You bought a guitar with your severance pay.

And you have enough savings to do without a job for a year.

So you've decided to devote some time to yourself.
